Seeker Stories covers what it’s like to
have a virtual relationship here.

00:03:20.660 --> 00:03:27.279
And if you haven’t found the perfect partner
who isn’t made of 1s and 0s, is it better

00:03:27.279 --> 00:03:28.919
to settle or be forever alone?

00:03:28.919 --> 00:03:48.209
Julia and Trace tell you what science has
to say in this episode.

00:03:48.209 --> 00:03:51.890
So would you risk feeling less satisfied with
your appearance if it meant striking a match?

